


---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/main.astro';
import { baseUrl } from '../lib/base-url';

const pageClass = 'about';
const title = 'About Us | Sustainable Talent';
const description = 'Not a staffing firm - a talent operating system. We run your contractor and recruiting engine end-to-end with TalentOS™ visibility.';
const ogImage = 'https://sustainabletalent.com/og-about.jpg';
const canonicalUrl = 'https://sustainabletalent.com/about';
---

<MainLayout 
  pageClass={pageClass}
  title={title}
  description={description}
  ogImage={ogImage}
  canonicalUrl={canonicalUrl}
>
<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-left">
        <div class="pill animated reveal">
          <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="text">Operators + TalentOS™</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="reveal">Not a staffing firm—<br/>a talent operating system</h1>
        <p class="subhead reveal">
          Sustainable Talent runs your contractor and recruiting engine end-to-end.
          TalentOS™ gives you visibility and control—our team delivers outcomes with enterprise-level rigor.
        </p>

        <div class="diff-block reveal">
          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="diff-head">What makes us different</div>
              <p class="diff-body">
                We don't "send resumes." We run the system: intake, calibration, velocity, compliance, onboarding,
                renewals, and reporting—with a platform layer you can actually see.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="diff-item">
            <div class="diff-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="diff-head">What leaders get</div>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Real-time program visibility (TalentOS™ dashboards)</li>
                <li>Predictable delivery cadence (weekly operating rhythm)</li>
                <li>Quality that scales (human-led, data-backed)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-row reveal">
          <a class="btn primary bounce-subtle" href="#get-started">Talk to us</a>
          <a class="btn primary bounce-subtle" href={`${baseUrl}/platform`}>Explore TalentOS™</a>
        </div>

        <div class="microproof reveal">
          If your team is tired of vendor chaos and spreadsheet governance, you're in the right place.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-right reveal scale-in">
        <div class="frame float-medium" role="img" aria-label="Sustainable Talent operating metrics">
          <div class="topbar">
            <div class="dots" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span>
            </div>
            <div>Delivery snapshot</div>
            <div class="chip"><span class="spark good pulse-glow"></span> Healthy</div>
          </div>

          <div class="frame-body">
            <div class="metric-grid">
              <div class="metric">
                <div class="metric-row">
                  <span>Employee satisfaction</span>
                  <span class="chip"><span class="spark good"></span> High</span>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-val">4.8/5</div>
                <div class="metric-trend">↑ 12% this quarter</div>
              </div>

              <div class="metric">
                <div class="metric-row">
                  <span>Submission → interview</span>
                  <span class="chip"><span class="spark"></span> Strong</span>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-val">35–45%</div>
                <div class="metric-trend">Industry avg: 18–22%</div>
              </div>

              <div class="metric metric-wide">
                <div class="metric-row">
                  <span>Program health</span>
                  <span class="chip"><span class="spark good"></span> Good</span>
                </div>
                <div class="health-bar" aria-hidden="true">
                  <div class="health-fill"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-val">98%</div>
              </div>

              <div class="metric">
                <div class="metric-row">
                  <span>Countries supported</span>
                  <span class="chip"><span class="spark"></span> Global</span>
                </div>
                <div class="metric-val">150+</div>
                <div class="metric-trend">Via Deel + ADP</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="frame-note">
              Real metrics from enterprise programs. Validated by actual delivery data.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS STRIP -->
<section class="stats-strip" aria-label="Key differentiators">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat reveal scale-in">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-num">98%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Customer satisfaction</div>
        <div class="stat-note">Enterprise-grade delivery and support</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat reveal scale-in">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-num">4.8/5</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Consultant satisfaction</div>
        <div class="stat-note">High-trust experience for talent and teams</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat reveal scale-in">
        <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-num">150+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Countries supported</div>
        <div class="stat-note">Global coverage through trusted partners</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OPERATING SYSTEM -->
<section class="section light" id="operating-system">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="kicker reveal">Our differentiator</p>

    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="pill animated" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="text">A real operating system</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="reveal">A real operating system—not "service"</h2>
    <p class="lead reveal">
      Anyone can promise speed. The difference is whether you can run the machine clean at scale.
      We combine operators + TalentOS™ so delivery is visible, measurable, and repeatable.
    </p>

    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card glass reveal scale-in" tabindex="0">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9" stroke-width="2"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">TalentOS™ visibility</div>
        <div class="card-body">Dashboards for open roles, pipeline stages, approvals, active consultants, renewals, and program health.</div>
        <div class="card-proof">No spreadsheet governance required.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card glass reveal scale-in" tabindex="0">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">Weekly operating rhythm</div>
        <div class="card-body">A consistent cadence that keeps decisions moving: calibration, funnel review, blockers, and next actions.</div>
        <div class="card-proof">Operators run the room—your team stays focused.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card glass reveal scale-in" tabindex="0">
        <div class="card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-title">Quality that scales</div>
        <div class="card-body">We protect experience and outcomes: structured screening, calibrated submissions, and clear feedback loops.</div>
        <div class="card-proof">High bar. Low drama.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="panel glass reveal slide-left" tabindex="0">
        <div class="panel-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-title">Operating principles</div>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Start with calibration, not volume</li>
          <li>Every role has a definition of "good" (documented)</li>
          <li>Feedback must be fast, specific, and actionable</li>
          <li>Compliance and experience are non-negotiable</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="panel-proof">This is how we stay fast without getting sloppy.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="panel glass reveal slide-right" tabindex="0">
        <div class="panel-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-title">What teams get out of it</div>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Cleaner decision-making (less back-and-forth)</li>
          <li>Improved submission → interview conversion</li>
          <li>Higher retention and renewal confidence</li>
          <li>Real program visibility for leadership</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="panel-proof">Great outcomes and a calmer process can coexist.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOUNDER NOTE -->
