  <div class="container">
    <p class="kicker reveal">A quick note</p>

    <div class="pill animated reveal" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
      <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      <span class="text">Why we built this</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="reveal">We built this the way we wish vendors worked</h2>

    <div class="founder-card glass reveal scale-in" tabindex="0">
      <div class="founder-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="founder">
        <div class="avatar zoom-on-hover">
          <img src="/team/69303157a3299c60a61695c9_Stephani Rodis.png" alt="Stephanie Rodis - Founder & CEO" loading="lazy" />
          <div class="avatar-ring"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="founder-content">
          <div class="founder-meta">
            <div class="founder-name">Stephanie Rodis</div>
            <div class="founder-role">Founder & CEO</div>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephanie-rodis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link" aria-label="Stephanie's LinkedIn">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="founder-body">
            We started Sustainable Talent to raise the bar on how hiring and extended workforce programs should run.
            Our belief is simple: enterprise-grade outcomes require enterprise-grade operations—but delivered with a human touch.
            We built TalentOS™ so you can see the engine, not just hear updates about it.
          </div>
          <div class="founder-quote">
            "If you want a partner that runs the work like it's internal, you'll feel at home here."
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

